                                        transactions of their lives.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col white-txt text-center">
                    <div class="card-flipper effect__hover" data-id="1">
                        <div class="card__front">
                            <div class="card card-01">
                                <div class="profile-box-01">
                                    <img
                                        class="card-img-top"
                                        src="/images/Katie.webp"
                                        alt="Card image cap"
                                    />
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body text-center">
                                    <h3 class="card-title">Katie Burnett</h3>
                                    <h4 class="card-text">Strategy Director</h4>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card__back">
                            <div class="card card-01">
                                <div class="card-body text-center">
                                    <h4 class="card-title">Katie Burnett</h4>
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        Katie is a highly accomplished marketing
                                        professional with a proven ability to
                                        turn concepts into tangible results. She
                                        has established herself as a trusted
                                        authority for our agents aiming to
                                        establish a strong presence in the
                                        competitive market. Katie’s enthusiasm
                                        for driving business success, coupled
                                        with her commitment to excellence and
                                        dedication to growth, guarantees that
                                        our agents confidently attain their
                                        marketing objectives.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col white-txt text-center">
                    <div class="card-flipper effect__hover" data-id="1">
                        <div class="card__front">
                            <div class="card card-01">
                                <div class="profile-box-01">
                                    <img
                                        class="card-img-top"
                                        src="/images/Liz.webp"
                                        alt="Card image cap"
                                    />
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body text-center">
                                    <h3 class="card-title">Liz Oakley, CRP</h3>
                                    <h4 class="card-text">
                                        Relocation Director
                                    </h4>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card__back">
                            <div class="card card-01">
                                <div class="card-body text-center">
                                    <h4 class="card-title">Liz Oakley, CRP</h4>
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        Liz is our Relocation and Corporate
                                        Services Director, with over 10 years of
                                        experience in being one of the best in
                                        the industry. She oversees the company’s
                                        relocation of corporate employees,
                                        federal law enforcement, military
                                        members, unions, schools and much more.
                                        All other lead generation systems. Due
                                        to her hard work and dedication, her
                                        teams have been awarded Platinum within
                                        the nation’s top networks.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="overlay-darker"></div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    hr {
        border: 1px solid white;
        opacity: 1;
    }
    button {
        background-color: #231f20;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.7em 1.5em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: 200;
        transition: 0.2s all ease-in-out;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: white;
        color: #231f20;
    }
    h4 {
        font-family: unset;
        font-size: 1.5em;
    }
    h3 {
        font-size: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 0em;
    }
    .title {
        font-size: 3vw;
    }
    .modal-content {
        background-color: #383838;
    }
    .close {
        border-radius: 50px;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        display: grid;
        place-content: center;
    }
    .form-group {
        padding: 0.5em 0em;
    }
    /*flipper-card*/
    .card-title {
        color: white;
    }
    .card-text {
        color: white;
    }
    .card {
        background-color: transparent;
        border: none;
    }
    .card-flipper {
        position: relative;
        float: left;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        /* height: 450px; */
    }

    .card__back {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        margin: auto;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: fit-content;
    }

    .card__back .card {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .card__front,
    .card__back {
        -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
        backface-visibility: hidden;
        -webkit-transition: 0.3s;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .card__front {
        background-color: transparent;
    }

    .card__back {
        background-color: #383838;
        border-radius: 20px;
        -webkit-transform: rotateY(-180deg);
        -ms-transform: rotateY(-180deg);
        transform: rotateY(-180deg);
    }
    .card-flipper.effect__hover:hover .card__front {
        -webkit-transform: rotateY(-180deg);
        -ms-transform: rotateY(-180deg);
        transform: rotateY(-180deg);
    }

    .card-flipper.effect__hover:hover .card__back {
        -webkit-transform: rotateY(0);
        -ms-transform: rotateY(0);
        transform: rotateY(0);
    }

    .card-flipper.effect__random.flipped .card__front {
        -webkit-transform: rotateY(-180deg);
        -ms-transform: rotateY(-180deg);
        transform: rotateY(-180deg);
    }

    .card-flipper.effect__random.flipped .card__back {
        -webkit-transform: rotateY(0);
        -ms-transform: rotateY(0);
        transform: rotateY(0);
    }
</style>
